; ConnectKit 1.9 declares peer react@"17.x || 18.x"; project is on Next 15
; with React 19. The runtime is compatible (ConnectKit's @aave/account
; transitive dep already accepts 19, ConnectKit just hasn't bumped its own
; peer range). legacy-peer-deps=true lets `npm ci` (used in CI) install
; without erroring out, matching what local `npm install --legacy-peer-deps`
; already does.
legacy-peer-deps=true
